{"tid":2501084,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉咗新工好伏，未有新offer 走唔走好","createTime":"2021-04-23T06:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:46:44.000Z","uid":88327,"like":98,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0161d539063138223a4ce47cc16f8a5a2be2fdca","tid":2501084,"uid":88327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"話說轉咗新工兩個星期，開始發現愈來愈唔對路<br />\n每個星期都有同事last day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同事話我呢個位係replacement ，同team本來有4個人，走咗3個...而家請返我1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作量唔係話好多（因為新入職咩系統都未開）<br />\n不過已經感受到好多有deadline 既野都過咗deadline先比我做...<br />\n<br />\n早兩日腦細照肺，叫我搵D新生意比公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（心諗：What?/舊野都未做得切，重想搵新？）又話我手腳慢，D job過晒期（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為你過咗期先比我做啫）<br />\n<br />\n已經send緊CV搵緊工，諗緊過唔過到下星期，驚到時又比腦細照肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如早D遞信，廢事拖兩拖又話過唔到試用期，寫花我CV"},{"pid":"f7ef9c63fda942551c694762ee7dfb3596238551","tid":2501084,"uid":52,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"2個星期就即走啦仲等咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544dfb1d4f77229d7961c3a2cba5205b007e748b","tid":2501084,"uid":31238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"即走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊行？"},{"pid":"23b6f8a228a26059cec3c81f3f1098cad492ebe6","tid":2501084,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"Junior定senior位？"},{"pid":"c4c3f81dc3828b59ba6eeca500b962b1a08ed162","tid":2501084,"uid":88327,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f7ef9c63fda942551c694762ee7dfb